      <c01 level="series">
        <did>
          <unittitle>Topical Files</unittitle>
        </did>
        <scopecontent>
          <p>The Topical Files comprise one series of alphabetically arranged subject files which document all aspects of the League's activities between 1955 and 1986. The bulk of these files document local issues at the municipal and county levels: included are materials generated by several committees of the Allen Park and Detroit Metropolitan Leagues (Housing Action Committee, Metro Integration Study Committee); studies of Allen Park (Charter Revision, Library Services, Recreational Facilities); and studies of Wayne County (Wayne County Home Rule Study). To a lesser extent, these files document state issues (State Constitutional Convention); as well as national and international issues.</p>
